# Cloudflare Tunnel token. Copy to cloudflared.env (gitignored) and paste the token.
#
# In the Cloudflare Zero Trust dashboard:
#   Networks -> Tunnels -> Create a tunnel -> choose "Cloudflared" -> copy the token.
# Then on that tunnel add a PUBLIC HOSTNAME:
#   Subdomain/domain: meta-mcp.<your-domain>   Service: http://meta-ads-mcp:8000
# (Your domain must be on Cloudflare. The tunnel auto-creates the DNS record.)
TUNNEL_TOKEN=paste_your_tunnel_token_here
